title: Search TV show (1972-1973)
description:
Search (1972-1973), was a great show which was overlooked by many as being too
far-fetched, and lasted only one season.  I prefer to think it was just ahead of
its time, and if made today would be more successful.

I searched in vain for this show on the internet for years, finding only a few
episodes originally captured with the primitive VCRs of the day.  (Typing
"Search" into a search engine is a little like trying to throw out a garbage
can--the guys refuse to take it!)

Finally at long long last the episodes were released to DVD in 2014, re-created
from the original film negatives.  I present them here for other fans of this
cool old high-tech adventure.

The original pilot movie was called Probe, (as the series was intended to be,
but that name was taken by an investigative news show on another network), and
is included also from another source.  It is a poorer, yet watchable, quality.

Enjoy
